PrecisOrder declining the petition of GEOPHYSICAL SERVICE INCORPORATED to vary or rescind CANADIAN TRANSPORTATION AGENCY DECISION NO. 216-W-2010 dated May 20, 2010, dealing with an application by PF Collins (on behalf of PGS Geophysical) for a licence to use a foreign flagged vessel (the Harrier Explorer) to conduct a 2D seismic survey in Canada's East Coast.
